                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-197-18341124 t18341124-197-punishment-191"></join>Confined One Month</rs>.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Sixth Jury, before Mr. Common Sergeant</hi>.</p>
